code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>Math.pow()</strong></code> 函数返回基数（<code>base</code>）的指数（<code>exponent</code>）次幂，即&nbsp;<code>base^exponent</code>。</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/math-pow.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>Math.pow(<em>base</em>, <em>exponent</em>) </code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"base\"><code>base</code></dt>\n <dd>基数</dd>\n <dt id=\"exponent\"><code>exponent</code></dt>\n <dd>指数</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>由于&nbsp;<code>pow</code>&nbsp;是&nbsp;<code>Math</code>&nbsp;的静态方法，所以应该像这样使用：<code>Math.pow()</code>，而不是作为你创建的&nbsp;<code>Math</code> 对象的方法。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_using_math.pow","title":"使用&nbsp;<code>Math.pow</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">raisePower</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>y</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>如果&nbsp;<code>x</code>&nbsp;是 2 ，且&nbsp;<code>y</code>&nbsp;是 7，则 raisePower 函数返回 128（2 的 7 次幂）。</p>","titleAsText":"使用 Math.pow"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范版本</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注解</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>ECMAScript 1st Edition. Implemented in JavaScript 1.0</td>\n   <td>Standard</td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.8.2.13\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Math.pow</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-math.pow\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Math.pow</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Math.pow","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/pow/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/cbrt\"><code>Math.cbrt()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/exp\"><code>Math.exp()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/log\"><code>Math.log()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Math/sqrt\"><code>Math.sqrt()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Arithmetic_Operators#Exponentiation\" title=\"Arithmetic operators take numerical values (either literals or variables) as their operands and return a single numerical value. The standard arithmetic operators are addition (+), subtraction (-), multiplication (*), and division (/).\">Exponentiation operator</a>&nbsp;<svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"描述","id":"description"},{"text":"示例","id":"examples"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Math.pow() 函数返回基数（base）的指数（exponent）次幂，即 base^exponent。","popularity":0.0018,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Math.pow()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/math/pow","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/math/pow/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","ti